Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: usb-audio: Skip generic sync EP parse for secondary EP
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: efb75df105e82f076a85b9f2d81410428bcb55fc
